Database Schema

This document describes the PostgreSQL schema for the BT.01 construction estimating and operations platform (Supabase). Tables are grouped by functional area. Foreign keys and generated columns are noted inline.


Note: schema is provided for reference — column order and constraints may not reflect exact execution order in the live database.




