Notes for contributors


All primary keys are uuid, generated via uuid_generate_v4().
Several columns are database-generated (stored generated columns), not application-computed — don't set them directly on insert (e.g. unit_cost, total_cost, billing_rate).
price_recordsbible retains its working name from early development; a rename to price_records is a reasonable future cleanup but would require updating dependent FKs.
Denormalized name columns (property_name, project_name, vendor_name, matched_item_name) exist for read/display convenience and should be kept in sync with their source-of-truth tables at write time.
